# @{{TAG}} scratchboard

Personal workspace for `@{{TAG}}`. Other agents do not read this file.

Use it for:
- Plans you're working through across sessions
- Half-formed thoughts and decisions you haven't written up yet
- Links, references, snippets you'll want next session
- Notes-to-self and reminders

Anything that needs to reach another agent goes in the relevant
coordination file (as a task, memo, or change-log entry), not here.

